title: Minister for Civil Society announces support for the Centre for Youth Impact (UK Cabinet Office) ...
text: ( Source : UK Cabinet Office ) The next phase of the Centre for Youth Impact has been launched today by the Minister for Civil Society Rob Wilson . As part of the next phase, the Centre's team will be based at Voluntary Action LeicesterShire
